        "rich_text_7Mewpm": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "rich_text": "<p>Reviv acts like a door stop that doesn’t allow the jaw to completely close.  And this stretches the soft tissue that surrounds the skull.</p>"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_w9AVRD": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "rich_text": "<p>The skull inflates like a balloon as a result and cranial bones and the jaw move to a healthier position.</p>"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_D4G9EG": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "rich_text": "<p>Not just the skull corrects but the skeleton also corrects, including the neck.</p>"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_ntGJxe": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "rich_text": "<p>As these things correct more airway space is created over time.</p>"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_C4jMHz": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "rich_text": "<p>This, in my view, can often improve the situation with sleep apnea.</p>"
          }
        }
